00:38:20.770 --> 00:38:21.620
The question then becomes

00:38:21.620 --> 00:38:23.553
what is the anatomical readout of this?

00:38:23.553 --> 00:38:26.290
And so you have, it's
behaving in the same way.

00:38:26.290 --> 00:38:27.123
So, here's a chick limb.

00:38:27.123 --> 00:38:29.020
Here's one when you treat
