00:38:29.020 --> 00:38:32.860
Again, you induce another ZPA,
a Sonic hedgehog expression.

00:38:32.860 --> 00:38:35.240
And what you see is here is the normal,

00:38:35.240 --> 00:38:37.520
and then in the treated ones,

00:38:37.520 --> 00:38:40.040
you find rays branching
out in the opposite side.

00:38:40.040 --> 00:38:44.770
For all intents and purposes,
being a mirror duplication.

00:38:44.770 --> 00:38:46.070
And we can dissect these things out,

00:38:46.070 --> 00:38:49.597
and characterize what these
duplicated rays look like.

00:38:49.597 --> 00:38:50.480
And for all the world,

00:38:50.480 --> 00:38:52.770
it looks like they're coming
